# Creators & Tipping

Zcash tools that empower creators to receive **private, shielded ZEC tips** directly from their audience. No platform fees, full self-custody, and maximum privacy using Zcash shielded transactions.

These platforms integrate with X (Twitter) for easy discovery and tipping, and support shielded Zcash unified addresses.

## 1. Zcash.me

**Website:** [https://zcash.me](https://zcash.me)

**Description:**  
Zcash.me is a simple profile directory and tipping platform for creators. Verify your X account, add your Zcash unified address, and get a public profile that makes it effortless for supporters to send shielded ZEC tips — including direct in-browser tipping on X via integrated wallets like Zucchini.

**Key Features:**
- X (Twitter) account verification + profile creation
- Add shielded Zcash unified address for receiving tips
- Public directory of verified creators (partial addresses shown for privacy)
- Easy discovery and tipping from social media
- In-browser shielded ZEC payments (powered by wallets like Zucchini)
- Fully non-custodial — tips go straight to your wallet

