## 2. TipZ (tipz.cash)

**Website:** [https://tipz.cash](https://tipz.cash)  
**Creator Directory:** [https://tipz.cash/creators](https://tipz.cash/creators)  
**Creator Dashboard:** [https://tipz.cash/my](https://tipz.cash/my)  
**GitHub (MIT license):** [https://github.com/tipz-cash/tipz.cash](https://github.com/tipz-cash/tipz.cash)

**Description:**  
TipZ is a live, non-custodial tipping platform built for creators and cypherpunks. Every tip arrives as shielded ZEC (100% to the creator). Supporters can send from any asset (ETH, USDC, USDT, SOL) — the platform bridges and shields it automatically. Zero platform fees, end-to-end encrypted messages, and powerful creator tools.

**Key Features:**
- Permissionless signup: connect X account + enter Zcash unified address (2 steps)
- Shareable tip page: `tipz.cash/yourhandle`
- Fully private ZEC-to-ZEC tipping (direct send or bridged)
- 0% platform fees + instant self-custody settlement (\~5 min)
- Encrypted private messages (only creator can decrypt)
- Real-time dashboard: total earnings (ZEC + USD), tip history, live updates
- Promotion tools: copy link, pre-filled tweets, image stamp generator
- Any-asset input bridged via NEAR Intents to shielded ZEC output
- Creator directory for easy discovery
- Powered by Zodl wallet & NEAR Intents
 
