## How to Get Started (for Creators)
1. Choose a platform above.
2. Verify your X account and add your **Zcash unified address** (shielded by default).
3. Share your tip page/link on social media.
4. Receive 100% of tips privately in your wallet (use Zashi, Zodl, Zecwallet, or any shielded-capable wallet).

**Pro Tip:** Always use shielded addresses for maximum privacy. Tips are non-custodial — the platforms never hold your funds.
